ActCopyright Modernization Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day that is Six Months after the Day on which this Order is published as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Copyright Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day that is six months after the day on which this Order is published in the Canada Gazette, Part II, as the day on which sections 41.25 and 41.26 and subsection 41.27(3) of the COPYRIGHT MODERNIZATION ACT, chapter 20 of the Statutes of Canada, 2012, COME INTO FORCE.
